{"tid":447080,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"做完激光矯視，你問我答","createTime":"2017-10-25T02:59:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-04T07:50:43.000Z","uid":26678,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"77478550f4061e19aedd19b1d45a6b7d578df638","tid":447080,"uid":26678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T02:59:57.000Z","msg":"10月10號做完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"863794bb45698c0ad4a59ccc877ddb61930c2eb1","tid":447080,"uid":18012,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T03:00:44.000Z","msg":"唔做微笑?"},{"pid":"b2866055751aee34718a0ae437c0e6887c2444c7","tid":447080,"uid":42487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T03:00:51.000Z","msg":"邊到做？ how much?"},{"pid":"2bf6b46b2df69868e379d3060e9660fc4cbe801b","tid":447080,"uid":18568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T03:02:04.000Z","msg":"為左咩而做？"},{"pid":"23f707b23a76c6ef01c2869d04fa0c4b3cc70d20","tid":447080,"uid":130162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T03:02:54.000Z","msg":"做之前有冇淆底<br />\n痛左幾耐"},{"pid":"6ea887a65984b629fea063a1d31c39353837e018","tid":447080,"uid":84212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T03:03:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3229736ac10baaf45da3ab52b135192e8bdf4b88","tid":447080,"uid":26678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T03:03:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔做微笑?</blockquote><br />\nLasik信譽好啲"},{"pid":"6657a070c2121f95c0f7e9a02147a695cc453528","tid":447080,"uid":26678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T03:04:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊到做？ how much?</blockquote><br />\n養和。<br />\n指定醫生差唔多三皮"},{"pid":"624c7ce20a57e14cd8475fd4a2d55da7092e7d75","tid":447080,"uid":38540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T03:04:28.000Z","msg":"點解唔等新技術成熟D再做 副作用少好多喎 激光老左好易青光"},{"pid":"569aa96f69ee62d7ca4a42f8c115289e4c99175d","tid":447080,"uid":26678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T03:04:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>為左咩而做？</blockquote><br />\n唔想戴眼鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 戴con戴得耐又乾"},{"pid":"33bc6d0cd87273664c4c9f7fedd14729f3371d16","tid":447080,"uid":26678,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T03:05:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做之前有冇淆底<br />\n痛左幾耐</blockquote><br />\n好撚淆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實唔痛 係麻醉過左之後好&quot;銀&quot;眼<br />\n訓醒就無事"},{"pid":"98cdee9a6c32e1998f7e63ea1b76fc20eb4a417c","tid":447080,"uid":25391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T03:05:51.000Z","msg":"隻眼見到強光會唔會好唔舒服"},{"pid":"088339b131b8170772ce3f4f32a7a6fedb0eaea7","tid":447080,"uid":77643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T03:06:38.000Z","msg":"幾歲？"},{"pid":"aad5880615279647375cc42c4d3ddf5ca4557d07","tid":447080,"uid":5519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T03:07:19.000Z","msg":"我都準備做 不過未book因爲好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7186b5dd7053e9e2e84b3dc2443f1e5aed51c0b2","tid":447080,"uid":26678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T03:09:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解唔等新技術成熟D再做 副作用少好多喎 激光老左好易青光</blockquote><br />\n我係忽然痴起條筋就做左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nResearch完一排就的起心肝去做<br />\n醫生話青光眼係本身隻眼有高度近視就會有風險，唔關激光事，最多度數反彈<br />\n<blockquote>後遺症有d咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家仲需要滴下人工淚水，無喇"},{"pid":"0bed5ba0dd37a016120fd4cfe83cb3bda584611a","tid":447080,"uid":26678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T03:10:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>隻眼見到強光會唔會好唔舒服</blockquote><br />\n唔會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過而家出戶外要戴一個月太陽眼鏡"},{"pid":"5213dd92a009854faae96dc224d574db6c479e8e","tid":447080,"uid":26678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T03:11:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都準備做 不過未book因爲好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我個陣都好撚驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實真正做個陣係乜柒都睇唔到<br />\n佢都比我聽住歌做，兩首歌時間就做完<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>幾歲？</blockquote><br />\n22"},{"pid":"2fb41129ee29fbb00087fb376daad6dea8f945cc","tid":447080,"uid":26678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T03:41:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0ae703f89e84026ab23c05996488e2ab160d3a0","tid":447080,"uid":138834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T03:54:21.000Z","msg":"做之前有冇考慮過另一隻新野<br />\n<br />\n好似話痴啲晶體入眼，視力變到仲好過正常人<br />\n<br />\n冇記錯就加拿大野嚟"},{"pid":"0b0569ae00acca38d122f765796a0fb594c6db71","tid":447080,"uid":130162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T03:58:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解唔等新技術成熟D再做 副作用少好多喎 激光老左好易青光</blockquote><br />\n我係忽然痴起條筋就做左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nResearch完一排就的起心肝去做<br />\n醫生話青光眼係本身隻眼有高度近視就會有風險，唔關激光事，最多度數反彈<br />\n<blockquote>後遺症有d咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家仲需要滴下人工淚水，無喇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你本身幾度近視？<br />\n我近視500，散光差唔多300<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我返工長期對電腦，如果做左好驚會反彈<br />\n而且淆底唔敢做"},{"pid":"65eebba0d2e1d1811c6331b3864a75177fa1103e","tid":447080,"uid":130141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T04:23:15.000Z","msg":"我幾年前做咗旺角果間，1萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做完幾爽，到宜家都冇咩後遺症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4338adf09349c116dd25fabf4271343885454a2f","tid":447080,"uid":26678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T04:39:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做之前有冇考慮過另一隻新野<br />\n<br />\n好似話痴啲晶體入眼，視力變到仲好過正常人<br />\n<br />\n冇記錯就加拿大野嚟</blockquote><br />\n有睇過，我覺得好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fff30151306c44cefaba5623378ca1063c885bdd","tid":447080,"uid":26678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T04:39:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解唔等新技術成熟D再做 副作用少好多喎 激光老左好易青光</blockquote><br />\n我係忽然痴起條筋就做左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nResearch完一排就的起心肝去做<br />\n醫生話青光眼係本身隻眼有高度近視就會有風險，唔關激光事，最多度數反彈<br />\n<blockquote>後遺症有d咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家仲需要滴下人工淚水，無喇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你本身幾度近視？<br />\n我近視500，散光差唔多300<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我返工長期對電腦，如果做左好驚會反彈<br />\n而且淆底唔敢做</blockquote><br />\n度數同你差唔多，我返工都係對電腦<br />\n做完世界一片光明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a72e77eb5ac186f6ce9922bef669735eec128276","tid":447080,"uid":26678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T04:40:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我幾年前做咗旺角果間，1萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做完幾爽，到宜家都冇咩後遺症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3825e9f1db38cc8a560ca6779f59c23807bb9247","tid":447080,"uid":29826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T04:49:04.000Z","msg":"想做但好撚驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ed551cd8dd284f56808fcd53660d750afd64854","tid":447080,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T04:59:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>10月10號做完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n幾多度?"},{"pid":"34227bf4f534c8c78ad3962ed2a3b6747a76b724","tid":447080,"uid":85751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T05:00:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解唔等新技術成熟D再做 副作用少好多喎 激光老左好易青光</blockquote><br />\n老左risk 大d喎"},{"pid":"40db5e5d26740f1606cea306f61052e8abaf8ab9","tid":447080,"uid":10586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T05:02:20.000Z","msg":"由有念頭做手術開始到第一次睇醫生直到做手術要幾耐時間？<br />\n會唔會有隻眼有冇啲特殊情況所以做唔到激光嘅案例？例如近視太淺太深或者飛蚊症"},{"pid":"c23eb73efa395b5140da444d865d0548c5e7d7a4","tid":447080,"uid":26678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T05:42:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>10月10號做完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n幾多度?</blockquote><br />\n500近視200散光"},{"pid":"8b73e30e4e25683e6fb08d875ebaa53b905b4f1d","tid":447080,"uid":26678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T05:43:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>由有念頭做手術開始到第一次睇醫生直到做手術要幾耐時間？<br />\n會唔會有隻眼有冇啲特殊情況所以做唔到激光嘅案例？例如近視太淺太深或者飛蚊症</blockquote><br />\n三個星期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n角膜太薄 眼水太少係唔做得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"653df0d707fd9d5294fdeb1ca1ef22bbb974cef9","tid":447080,"uid":26678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T05:46:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想做但好撚驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我覺得搣返撐開眼瞼個固定器落黎個陣好撚痛就真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fb92642253fed77325796d807e7e4836229e0e7","tid":447080,"uid":85025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T05:48:29.000Z","msg":"5，6年前做左<br />\n到而家都無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d58f77ebf344461566013f367f7b65bafea1098","tid":447080,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T05:50:23.000Z","msg":"點解唔做icl?"},{"pid":"911691c27f734f3f91f74fb003953cb53471e36a","tid":447080,"uid":25295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T05:52:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解唔做icl?</blockquote><br />\n我諗價錢都係其中一個考慮因素"},{"pid":"f4c805e173ab814ac60449cf94e9dcc3c48c5699","tid":447080,"uid":132736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T05:55:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我幾年前做咗旺角果間，1萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做完幾爽，到宜家都冇咩後遺症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打係做左幾多年？旺角邊間？"},{"pid":"19cc8afde28ac50c9b689d112556203a2609cfe5","tid":447080,"uid":10586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T05:55:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>由有念頭做手術開始到第一次睇醫生直到做手術要幾耐時間？<br />\n會唔會有隻眼有冇啲特殊情況所以做唔到激光嘅案例？例如近視太淺太深或者飛蚊症</blockquote><br />\n三個星期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n角膜太薄 眼水太少係唔做得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁一旦有下面呢兩種情況係咪可以做微笑取代？<br />\n因為遲啲想考份工一定唔可以有近視一定要做<br />\n但係好驚做唔到激光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9c748251556fd36e0340e29a445436b7f762b1d","tid":447080,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T05:57:51.000Z","msg":"1萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7dde2c0c30b79ccbe8d3f086886863e1ce9b361","tid":447080,"uid":117225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T05:58:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>為左咩而做？</blockquote><br />\n唔想戴眼鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 戴con戴得耐又乾</blockquote><br />\n用殖水凝膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"589790a4db4888b07f1445a2584f84c0476121e7","tid":447080,"uid":26678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T06:05:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>由有念頭做手術開始到第一次睇醫生直到做手術要幾耐時間？<br />\n會唔會有隻眼有冇啲特殊情況所以做唔到激光嘅案例？例如近視太淺太深或者飛蚊症</blockquote><br />\n三個星期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n角膜太薄 眼水太少係唔做得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁一旦有下面呢兩種情況係咪可以做微笑取代？<br />\n因為遲啲想考份工一定唔可以有近視一定要做<br />\n但係好驚做唔到激光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n微笑我無做過唔清楚要求<br />\n你直接去驗眼啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 會驗好仔細驗清楚你適唔適合做"},{"pid":"53f1b376a6d2084e90f3424f6beed7ab2b80928e","tid":447080,"uid":92882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T06:05:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d156cbe4e3c42a0d528464a9c230c25cfd1f37ac","tid":447080,"uid":26678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T06:06:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解唔做icl?</blockquote><br />\n搞個晶體好似好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3b0d8c3c9f56957594fef8667a5f88d9f376323","tid":447080,"uid":55296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T06:07:23.000Z","msg":"1200 度近視做唔做得"},{"pid":"fe35c5856875595f51fd0d98798b46bc05daec67","tid":447080,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T06:12:45.000Z","msg":"做果時眼球如果4圍碌有冇事？<br />\n點樣撐到唔4圍碌？"},{"pid":"b27a943fc4fb890ec508befbb023f07819e4de2d","tid":447080,"uid":26678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T06:18:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做果時眼球如果4圍碌有冇事？<br />\n點樣撐到唔4圍碌？</blockquote><br />\n事就唔會有，啲激光會追蹤你眼球<br />\n但醫生會指示你叫你望返住綠光"},{"pid":"1170f9a9ecc662aa47b6e7aa4a978a960a7d26a8","tid":447080,"uid":26678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T06:21:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1200 度近視做唔做得</blockquote><br />\n最高就係1200度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02285d368c24293781670bd14120f1575bef456c","tid":447080,"uid":398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T06:27:45.000Z","msg":"做完可唔可以做激烈運動<br />\n