080,"uid":44814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T06:40:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>5，6年前做左<br />\n到而家都無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n純分享<br />\n個friend做左 有隻眼視力接近冇左</blockquote><br />\n咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n矯視手術失敗左 詳細唔知"},{"pid":"d9dec955e1dfa2975c26df5d0b9364f51fbf6f61","tid":447080,"uid":26678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T07:10:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做完可唔可以做激烈運動<br />\n當然 做完手術一排 抖夠後</blockquote><br />\n有機會碰撞到隻眼既要停六個月（例如boxing）<br />\n游水停一個月"},{"pid":"d243ceb5d8f57ccde33417678f8bd1b9c3afc6ae","tid":447080,"uid":26678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T07:11:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽講老左會有問題喎</blockquote><br />\n而家醫學進步左應該無事既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e42dc45dc6f85e89b6eafb855b280f5dd20bb88","tid":447080,"uid":26678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T07:13:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>5，6年前做左<br />\n到而家都無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n純分享<br />\n個friend做左 有隻眼視力接近冇左</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁唔好彩<br />\n佢係做Lasik定smile？"},{"pid":"be6def72293ed49179afab401ab16b1c353abdba","tid":447080,"uid":44814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T07:15:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>5，6年前做左<br />\n到而家都無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<b